# Customer Segmentation Analysis

## Objective
Segment customers based on spending behavior and purchase frequency.

## Tools Used
- SQL
- Excel

## Approach
- Calculated total spending per customer
- Measured order frequency
- Categorized customers into segments

## Segments
- High Value Customers
- Medium Value Customers
- Low Value Customers

## Outcome
Helps businesses target high-value customers and improve marketing strategies.
